subtitle: as we wait and watch for infinite change
that cannot be stopped let us look
together today at aspects of life that
could assist you with A New Perspective
in an ocean of ever increasing
momentum if this was the last week of
your waking dream what would you change
what words would you speak and what
would you do differently what would
matter that does not have your attention
in this moment and what would not matter
at all even though it is all consuming
